roast @chickpeas{} and @broccolli{} in oven. season with tumeric

make a @yogurt{} by mixing yogurt, @ginger{} and @tumeric{}

fry chopped @shallot{} until golden add @chilli{} pepper and @garlic{} then add @peanuts{} and @mustard seeds{} then sprinkle on @lime{} juice.

plate the yogurt, then the broccolli and chickpeas then the shallot mix.
